rows.label: qst201405_msg0025
rows.name: No one's passing by...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0026
rows.name:
I guess everyone's resting in their
rooms instead of walking around...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0001
rows.name:
Since it's boring, let's
chat. About the favorite
food topic I asked Nia!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0027
rows.name:
Fine. What's your
favorite food, Zakuro?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0002
rows.name: My favorite food is Fleur Bavarois!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0003
rows.name:
With the white flower inside,
and its wobbly appearance...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0004
rows.name:
And the smoothness and sweetness you
feel when it's on your tongue...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0005
rows.name:
It's no exaggeration to say
it's a lump of Girl Power
itself! A true dessert!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0006
rows.name:
Hey, isn't that a bit
of an exaggeration?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0007
rows.name: Oh? Then what about you, Hikari?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0008
rows.name:
My favorite food is Cloud
Sea Crab Cream Croquettes!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0009
rows.name: ...Excuse me?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0010
rows.name:
Crispy on the outside,
fluffy on the inside!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0011
rows.name:
It's a delicious dish that
fully utilizes the Cloud
Sea Crab ingredient!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0012
rows.name:
No, no, no... Croquettes?
Seriously, not croquettes.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0013
rows.name:
That choice is way too low
in Girl Power, Hikari.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0014
rows.name:
What's wrong with Cloud Sea
Crab Cream Croquettes?!
They're super delicious!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0015
rows.name:
And your choice of sweets,
Zakuro, is so straightforward
it's almost calculating!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0016
rows.name: I'm still confident I beat croquettes!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0017
rows.name: So I have more Girl Power, right?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0018
rows.name: No way!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0019
rows.name:
Besides, it's pointless
without a judge!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0020
rows.name:
And this was just small
talk, right? Don't just
turn it into a competition!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0021
rows.name: Well, that's true...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0022
rows.name: Hmm, I wish someone would come soon.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0024
rows.name: We have to settle this next time!
